verses.text:
I have found a friend in Je-sus, He's ev-'ry thing to me, He's the fair-est of ten thou-sand to my soul;
The Lil-y of the Val-ley, in Him a-lone I see All I need to cleanse and make me ful-ly whole.
In sor-row He's my com-fort, in trou-ble He's my stay, He tells me ev-'ry care on Him to roll.
